я, Великобритания, его отцу по имени John de Swinburne было 26 лет, а матери, которую звали Avicia de Umfreville, 21. Он женился на женщине по имени Mrs. Margaret De Swinburne около 1259 г. в местности кафитон, нортумбирланд, Англия. У них было по крайней мере 2 сына и 1 дочь. Он умер в 1284 г. в возрасте 49 лет."},"sm":{"1235–1284":"1235–1284","1232–1324":"1232–1324","1237–1318":"1237–1318","1240–1279":"1240–1279","1239–1282":"1239–1282","1260–1309":"1260–1309","1273–1326":"1273–1326","1279–Male":"1279–Ua Maliu","1210–1301":"1210–1301","1215–1313":"1215–1313","about 1260":"e tusa o le 1260","1273":"1273","1284":"1284","1240":"1240","1282":"1282","1260":"1260","1239":"1239","1326":"1326","1215":"1215","1237":"1237","1313":"1313","1324":"1324","1235":"1235","1279":"1279","1301":"1301","about 1259":"e tusa o le 1259","1232":"1232","1210":"1210","1309":"1309","1318":"1318","Capheaton, Northumberland, England":"Capheaton, Northumberland, Egelani","Capheaton,Kirk Whelpington,Northumberland,England":"Kirkwhelpington, Northumberland, Egelani, United Kingdom","Swinburne Castle, Chollerton, Northumberland, England":"Chollerton, Northumberland, Egelani, United Kingdom","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, Egelani, United Kingdom"},"sk":{"1235–1284":"1235–1284","1232–1324":"1232–1324","1237–1318":"1237–1318","1240–1279":"1240–1279","1239–1282":"1239–1282","1260–1309":"1260–1309","1273–1326":"1273–1326","1279–Male":"1279–Zosnulý","1210–1301":"1210–1301","1215–1313":"1215–1313","about 1260":"okolo 1260","1273":"1273","1284":"1284","1240":"1240","1282":"1282","1260":"1260","1239":"1239","1326":"1326","1215":"1215","1237":"1237","1313":"1313","1324":"1324","1235":"1235","1279":"1279","1301":"1301","about 1259":"okolo 1259","1232":"1232","1210":"1210","1309":"1309","1318":"1318","Capheaton, Northumberland, England":"Capheaton, Northumberland, England","Capheaton,Kirk Whelpington,Northumberland,England":"Kirkwhelpington, Northumberland, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Swinburne